// E2E fixture: Supervisor with initialize: hook that wires children (BT-1542).
// initialize: calls which: on a sibling — would deadlock without caller-side dispatch.

Supervisor subclass: E2EInitSupervisor

  class children => #(E2EInitChildA, E2EInitChildB)

  class initialize: sup =>
    childA := sup which: E2EInitChildA
    childA setValue: 42
